name: Lacus Clyne | 机动战士高达SEED 拉克丝·克莱因 | ラクス・クライン (Mobile Suit Gundam SEED)
description:
There are 3 versions for different outfits! I separate them to make more consistent generation outputs.

To replace the preset outfit with others (e.g. school uniform), please use the black kimono ver.

Highres fix is strongly recommended for all 3 versions and I'm using ESRGAN_4x with denoise strength=0.5 for these samples.

white coat purple kimono ver.

LORA for character with anime original white coat and purple kimono. It's less consistent (on coloring part) comparing to previous 2 outfit.

Trigger words: 1girl lacus clyne pink hair blue eyes

Outfit: ponytail open clothes vest uniform long sleeves purple sleeves purple kimono japanese clothes

white and purple skirt ver.

LORA for character with anime original white and purple skirt. I found it more consistent when the LORA is focusing on one single outfit, but it still can not reproduce the outfit 100% correct, especially on the lower part of the dress😢.

Trigger words: 1girl lacus clyne pink hair blue eyes

Outfit: straight hair white sleeves detached sleeves purple skirt purple frills

black kimono ver.

A requested character LORA for Lacus Clyne from Mobile Suit Gundam SEED! Suggested weights: 1

Character trigger words: 1girl lacus clyne blue eyes pink hair

Hair style: straight hair or ponytail

Outfit triggers (less consistent in realistic models): japanese clothes black kimono detached sleeves
